follow cuda documents

ubuntu
download deb version installer

do the pre-installation checkings

go to download directory

$ sudo dpkg -i cuda-repo-<distro>_<version>_<architecture>.deb
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install cuda

add cuda into environment path,do not directly copy this command from document, manually write these command into cmdline
or might damage the system environment path
export PATH=/usr/local/cuda-8.0/bin${PATH:+:${PATH}}
